start:
Hi! Thanks for using TGSharp :heart:
Type /help to get list of commands :star:
commands:
Command list (type /help [command without prefix] to get info about command):
/type - Type text
/typef - Instantly type text
/screenshot - Take screenshot
/move - Move mouse cursor
/run - Run program
/runbg - Run program in background
/download - Download file
